- Not happening.

1279
01:27:38.200 --> 01:27:41.272
Get her to get us the personnel file
for Erin Manning.

1280
01:27:41.480 --> 01:27:42.800
She's not gonna do that.

1281
01:27:42.960 --> 01:27:45.873
